value: Remove the duplicates and put them in a separate list

title: solution
value:
var number_list = [19, 17, 12, 17, 17, 18, 10, 17, 14, 12, 19, 17, 12, 13, 11]
uniques=[]
duplicates=[]
for(var i of number_list){
if(!uniques.includes(i)){
uniques.push(i)
}
}

for(var j of uniques){
count=0
for(var k of number_list){
if (j === k){
count+=1
}
}
if(count >1){
duplicates.push(j);
};
}

console.log(duplicates);
